Hull_diff","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.html#convexIndependent_iff_not_mem_convexHull_diff","doc":"If a family is convex independent, a point in the family is not in the convex hull of the other\npoints. See `convexIndependent_set_iff_not_mem_convexHull_diff` for the `Set` version. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.lean#L128-L130","name":"ConvexIndependent.mem_convexHull_iff","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.html#ConvexIndependent.mem_convexHull_iff","doc":"If a family is convex independent, a point in the family is in the convex hull of some of the\npoints given by a subset of the index type if and only if the point's index is in this subset. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.lean#L116-L122","name":"Function.Injective.convexIndependent_iff_set","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.html#Function.Injective.convexIndependent_iff_set","doc":"The range of an injective indexed family of points is convex independent iff that family is. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.lean#L110-L112","name":"ConvexIndependent.mono","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.html#ConvexIndependent.mono","doc":"A subset of a convex independent set of points is convex independent as well. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.lean#L99-L106","name":"ConvexIndependent.range","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.html#ConvexIndependent.range","doc":"If an indexed family of points is convex independent, so is the corresponding set of points. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.lean#L93-L95","name":"ConvexIndependent.subtype","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.html#ConvexIndependent.subtype","doc":"If a family is convex independent, so is any subfamily indexed by a subtype of the index type.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.lean#L84-L88","name":"ConvexIndependent.comp_embedding","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.html#ConvexIndependent.comp_embedding","doc":"If a family is convex independent, so is any subfamily given by composition of an embedding into\nindex type with the original family. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.lean#L75-L79","name":"ConvexIndependent.injective","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.html#ConvexIndependent.injective","doc":"A convex independent family is injective. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.lean#L67-L71","name":"Subsingleton.convexIndependent","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.html#Subsingleton.convexIndependent","doc":"A family with at most one point is convex independent. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.lean#L60-L61","name":"ConvexIndependent","kind":"def","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Independent.html#ConvexIndependent","doc":"An indexed family is said to be convex independent if every point only belongs to convex hulls\nof sets containing it. "}]}